reviews: Works well.

It will stick to my eyelid more than the lash, and it's hard to get off even with makeup remover. Black colour should blend in better with lashes and eyeliner, but this is more of a grey, not black. Still works.
A little wobbly, but great brightness for what you pay. HOWEVER, the phone holder constantly slips down, and needs a more secure attachment.
Lovely colour, sturdy case with a great holder for your apple pen. Doesn't stand up as well as I'd like though.
Cleaning up drawings, using references, animating etc. are all things you can do with this, and for the price it's an affordable investment.
They don't last me longer than a year typically, but are comfortable and prevent you from dropping your phone on your face. A little expensive for what it is.
Nice video and audio quality, and super easy setup with the adjustable mount. Looks sleek on top of monitor.

Satisfying clack-y noise, great customization options with Synapse, and comfortable.
I do find I miss a key here or there because I'm used to a more condensed laptop keyboard.
Nice for gaming, chatting on Discord, homework, etc.

review_title: Size up if you got a big booty
reviews:
I am usually a small, but I got a medium and am glad I did. :)
Bought for a halloween party that I didn't end up going to. Oh well.

The only better mouse would be a fluffy real one.
But this mouse has great customization options with Synapse, and super comfortable with a great range of DPI.
Ordered for my brother's vinyl collection. He likes it!

I ordered this one for my ex. I would give my ex negative stars, but this case is great.
I have the same case and it lasted me years before eventually cracking around the edge, for good reasons (I throw my phone around quite a bit on the farm). Durable, chunky yet not too big to fit in a pocket, and looks cool.
Bring back the 80s :D

For my headset, I needed to plug the USB directly into my laptop or else it would cut in and out.
Other things such as webcam, keyboard, and mouse worked fine! The on/off buttons are a nice touch.
Good cord length if you need something to plug in behind a dresser. Lots of space for the many lights in my room and chargers.

review_title: Embrace your VSCO girl, or whatever
reviews:
The spray isn't as fine or misty as I'd like. Watch out if you try set makeup with this, as you will probably get a few fat droplets from it.
For a refreshing spray, it's nice. I like the green and pink one's smell, but the purple is a little weird.
If you're gonna be basic, might as well get this hat because it looks great on literally everybody.
Beautiful purple blanket. I use it as a throw instead of getting a new comforter to match my purple themed bedroom. Very soft.
So happy with it <3 Must-have game!
Comfortable, super adjustable, and a good accessory to take a grunge outfit to the next level.
What more is there to say? Good!

Bright purple lights with multiple settings for flashing, twinkling, etc. Note that if you select purple, that's the only colour it will turn!
Makes my room have a beautiful purple glow.

Note: the piece you get may not stand up well on its own, or be as intricate as the product picture shows.

However, that's to be expected buying a chunk of wood online that you can't see, and I propped mine up with some stones. It turns your water dark, but after a few water changes the tannins fade. Fish like tannins so don't worry about that, but be sure to check for any "stowaways" before adding this to your aquarium.

Wood secretes proteins that my snail love to munch, and my betta likes swimming about and resting on it. It also looks beautiful! I stuck some aquatic plants too it and tied their roots around it to stay in place, and it looks gorgeous.

WARNING: check for splinters first. Mine didn't have any, but you don't want to risk a fishy ripping their fin. :)

This mousepad fits my Razer mouse and keyboard comfortably. You can pick through different colours to match your setup. I like it, it sits flat on my desk and there is plenty of room to move my mouse around.

Note: this WILL make your water cloudy. DON'T rinse it first! The sediment is natural and will settle, this stuff is coated with minerals good for plants.

I have had great success with both germinating seeds underwater, and growing existing plants with this substrate. The reddish colouring looks beautiful in contrast with green.

Don't want to stir up red clouds every time you clean your tank? Surround your plants, driftwood, decor etc with bigger stones so they don't fall over, and keep in place.
My female betta loves to chase these as they sink, and her scales have gotten very colourful. She says they're delicious! 10/10 fishy approved.
Love the cover and colours inside. Lots of space to write notes, and a pleasing aesthetic.
Put on top of my 2.5 tank. Plants love it. It has a nice blue night mode, and the day mode is bright enough to grow greenery fairly quickly. Easy to extend and fit on rim of tank, and feels secure.
Fit my switch, super cute and easy to install.

review_title: Would Have Passed If I'd Known the Issues
reviews:
Note: remote does not come with batteries.

The "calming" sound quality is poor and audio segments reply jarringly, not a peaceful experience. The lights also move a little mechanically, and not smoothly if you watch it closely.

If you can get past that by muting the audio and enjoying the pretty lights, you will appreciate it. HOWEVER, the motion of it tilting to get that ocean-y motion makes a slight whirring noise. If it weren't for my music and aquarium filters running, I would single out the noise and find it annoying.

Still, I'm too lazy to return it, and it is quite pretty.

A beautiful floor for my planted 20 gallon, with only snails currently.
I use fluorite as substrate. The tank is heated, and lit with bright LEDs

PROS
Bright green, lush, germinated within 3 days. Super simple.

CONS
I would like some more seed for the price. Or price it cheaper?

review_title: pretty design doesn't hold up to time
reviews: Arrived on time. The red flowers turned out to be more of a faded burgundy. After several weeks, the case started to yellow and the colors age. It was very pretty at first, but didn't stand the test of time. :( Durability was average.

Arrived on time. I love this tapestry. It's true to dimensions and really adds a great vibe to my bedroom. Fabric is thin and lightweight, easily held up by thumbtacks. Goes well with cozy, earthy decor and plants.
Arrived on time. I love gummy sharks and these were soft and tasty. They got eaten fast, alas, now my gummy sharks are extinct.
